{"title":"号声一响万户开","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声一响万户开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声一响万户开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少奔出来；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口令三声千锄举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连营班排赴田野。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星班排往西冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火箭营连向东进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围歼害虫和野草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼已经消灭尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳遍西月东升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下锄头磨刀锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀闪光人影动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四野一片练武声。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}